data.description: Welcome to 1406 S 25th St! This 4 bedroom 2 bath beauty is ready to become your own little piece of heaven. This home is located in a beautiful developed subdivision with over 2000 sq feet! There is an attached 2 car garage with remote access to open and close garage doors, living room with electric fireplace, open living - dining area and a kitchen with breakfast bar containing granite countertops. The laundry room has built in cabinets and a folding counter. Master suite has a walk-in-closet with Ein suite which includes a jacuzzi tub, walk in shower with his and her sinks. Exterior of the home has outstanding mature landscaping with front and back sprinkler system, large covered patio perfect for entertaining friends and family. Make this beautiful home yours today! Call your favorite realtor to see it today!!
